20584acf-3712-4810-94fd-94c77c90d926.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make a green "spiral." Begin in the upper left corner and work clockwise around the outer edges of the grid. Turn clockwise one cell short of making a complete border of green. Continue coloring green until you reach the center of the grid.
20584acf-3712-4810-94fd-94c77c90d926.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input.
20584acf-3712-4810-94fd-94c77c90d926.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black background.

232e4c80-bdfd-4d6f-9594-84578c0fd4a9.do_description: To make the output, you have to...create a green pattern. Start in the upper left and go right. Hit the corner and go down. Continue in clockwise order. When you hit green, stop one blocks away and continue in the pattern. End in the center.
232e4c80-bdfd-4d6f-9594-84578c0fd4a9.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as input
232e4c80-bdfd-4d6f-9594-84578c0fd4a9.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid

61b9f8fe-c783-478b-8090-53013e5b61b3.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use green blocks to make and follow around the grid. Begin at the top left corner and keep go until you reach the center. Leave a black blocks between each row and of green and never let the green meet other than horizontally in the center on a grid with even horizontal row number.
61b9f8fe-c783-478b-8090-53013e5b61b3.grid_description: The output grid size...can stay the same.
61b9f8fe-c783-478b-8090-53013e5b61b3.see_description: In the input, you should see...an all black grid.
